snippet.textDisplay: Brilliant- absolutely mesmerizing. At 2:45 the lyrics actually says  "turiya" which has been misinterpreted as "dariya" in the captions. The mention of "Turiya" signifies an important link between Sufism and Vedanta philosophy. Turiya is a state of pure consciousness that is achieved in the state of samadhi. It's amazing how this word found its way into Sufi music.
